            . I am servant to Mr. Webb, at the corner of the Old Change. I delivered the linen ( mentioning them) to 
               <persName id="t17690906-87-person855">
                  Thomas 
                  Hawkins 
               <interp inst="t17690906-87-person855" type="surname" value="Hawkins"></interp>
